<h2 local-id=3D"3b9eb72d347e" id=3D"Upgraderoomforloyaltymembers(flow)-Over=
view">Overview</h2>
<p local-id=3D"41b14981ae91">The <strong>Upgrade Room for Loyalty Members</=
strong> flow automates the process of upgrading rooms for arriving guests b=
ased on loyalty status and configurable criteria. It runs on a schedule (da=
ily by default), identifies today's eligible arrivals, attempts to upgrade =
their assigned room category, and then handles the results =E2=80=94 sendin=
g an SMS to guests whose rooms were successfully upgraded, and adding a not=
e to reservations where the upgrade could not be completed so that hotel st=
aff are informed.</p>
<p local-id=3D"ab0dba9097a7">This flow is designed to be nearly ready to us=
e out of the box. Most fields come pre-configured with sensible defaults. <=
strong>Only one setting is mandatory before the flow can run:</strong> you =
must configure the <strong>Upgrade Path</strong> in the Upgrade Assigned Ro=
om Category component to define which room categories should be upgraded an=
d to which target categories.</p>
<hr local-id=3D"c867b0be-098f-4579-9da4-f6a309714c20">
<h2 local-id=3D"6b9ecd115141" id=3D"Upgraderoomforloyaltymembers(flow)-Befo=
reYouStart">Before You Start</h2>
<p local-id=3D"a6e3133dbe42"><strong>Required setup:</strong> Before starti=
ng the flow, you must configure the <strong>Upgrade Path</strong> in the <s=
trong>Upgrade Assigned Room Category</strong> component. This defines which=
 room categories are eligible for an upgrade and what the target category i=
s for each. Without this configuration, the flow will not know how to upgra=
de rooms.</p>
<p local-id=3D"9cb5cc3b5bee">All other settings in the flow come pre-filled=
 with default values and are ready to use. You can customize any of them to=
 match your property's needs =E2=80=94 see the component-by-component break=
down below for details on what can be adjusted.</p>
<hr local-id=3D"2cba0ee4-f0b2-46b5-bdf4-ccd258ec740d">
<h2 local-id=3D"cb2b6e775432" id=3D"Upgraderoomforloyaltymembers(flow)-Howt=
heFlowWorks">How the Flow Works</h2>
<p local-id=3D"53900aeb0c46">The flow consists of seven components connecte=
d in sequence, with branching logic to handle successful and failed upgrade=
s separately:</p>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-layout=3D"default" data-local-id=3D"b91aad6b-3d20-40be-a497-bbb=
36b4eee7d" class=3D"confluenceTable">
<tbody>
<tr data-local-id=3D"4e63a4c5-7fe4-4175-96a0-c7bf3cabcc35">
<th data-local-id=3D"ab43dacb-3750-4064-ba29-fc9752c1d0ce" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"6b1ef6c838d4">Step</p></th>
<th data-local-id=3D"0d8230a9-fc32-49d6-ab47-92867f6381d9" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"afa58340a63c">Component</p></th>
<th data-local-id=3D"ad2bb448-548f-494a-9772-935a4ffa45fa" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"2c14558ed389">Connects to</p></th>
<th data-local-id=3D"90973884-445d-4d21-897f-df66d8df99af" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"c8763e58c645">Description</p></th>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"5a0944a9-7be9-4be0-b1ea-188579f4514a">
<td data-local-id=3D"0a9692a3-9500-4e2f-ab14-26735768e374" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"53294be23ad7">1</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"81a3b5c9-0346-49bf-951d-4f8a55ab904f" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"4adca445a5ac">Cron Scheduler</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"c965c97a-3f78-4a21-998a-e78a4c2a8e3d" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"92ec7b5aee59">=E2=86=92 Step 2</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"b84bce4b-71d4-4c2e-b474-533f67d070dd" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"d50c09027eba">Triggers the flow on a recurring schedule (dai=
ly at noon by default).</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"30c477a6-1555-4375-a26a-75e0a0e22117">
<td data-local-id=3D"9de8339f-b896-4cd4-91f6-705a1d17b6fb" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"6f908f67e444">2</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"82627d12-99eb-45db-a38b-1cd06aa431d0" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"7ae506e8f61d">Check Occupancy</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"3f8164c4-ce06-48e1-b206-169aac89d8dd" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"d4156d4ad1d9"><em>Below threshold</em> =E2=86=92 Step 3</p><=
/td>
<td data-local-id=3D"369904c9-c68b-4858-b5ff-145f6e1b1412" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"036020224c56">Checks whether the property's occupancy is bel=
ow a configured threshold. If occupancy is at or above the threshold, the f=
low stops =E2=80=94 no upgrades are attempted when the property is fully oc=
cupied.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"076d6a71-a81c-48ea-a180-7edd94ca3f79">
<td data-local-id=3D"64ed85cc-6f10-41b6-ad1f-6ccde33a752f" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"5489eea7d937">3</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"1dbf3d48-9ec1-471b-9054-c9ff49f51de9" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"7b53cebb1137">Get Eligible Arrivals</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"8135c5f7-7b4c-40ae-bc50-cde09e99d0dc" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"0ade1913fabd">=E2=86=92 Step 4</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"204ec292-cfbb-4fb5-b636-65798edcced9" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"f940ad09df7d">Retrieves confirmed reservations arriving on t=
he target date, optionally filtered by loyalty program membership, behavior=
al signals, or rate codes.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"e62789a9-d65c-4c60-b091-21648322dee6">
<td data-local-id=3D"5667ba21-73e6-41d7-a5ac-ae7d6a62ac3d" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"f062c82ba332">4</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"ee22dd69-4e32-4943-9aa0-a1071fb8cf17" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"03966a39d172">Upgrade Assigned Room Category</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"f8460b68-4991-4042-966f-b00e5ecc08cb" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"84c5432fc16b"><em>Upgraded</em> =E2=86=92 Step 5<br><em>Fail=
ed</em> =E2=86=92 Step 7</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"ecfaa836-67b4-4e68-aff5-8dea294394c2" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"e61a24a8f405">Attempts to upgrade the room category for each=
 eligible reservation based on the configured upgrade paths and real-time a=
vailability. Results are split into two branches.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"46038ab0-5fc6-4595-8612-e19fe6e7bec7">
<td data-local-id=3D"1087cfb0-a39c-4fc0-932f-4dc2da2ccb13" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"1aa724cd2ff1">5</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"66113987-d3a9-43fa-96be-6170d5bda2b5" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"d00df1a9ddab">Each (Iterator)</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"718ea024-d506-4fb6-89cf-ef83444edc9b" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"66e2fddea54f">=E2=86=92 Step 6</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"3855ee4c-fd0e-446f-a57e-78aaafb0bb08" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"0239297bc801">Iterates over the list of successfully upgrade=
d reservations and triggers the next step for each one individually.</p></t=
d>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"9819c02d-b452-476a-b192-2741299db105">
<td data-local-id=3D"cc079bb1-15e2-46ce-896c-dc8c165e2441" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"0eb2b82574ab">6</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"1cc01b4b-4b0a-4a10-a29b-5d914aac81b0" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"b9193617e43c">Send SMS</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"61ec4413-24ac-4bea-a1d8-043bbc89e403" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"d59b655cd4b8"><em>End of branch</em></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"21ab6683-a81a-4d70-900b-0e2f96e2bd5a" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"a8f36eb40c94">Sends an SMS notification to each guest whose =
room was successfully upgraded.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"83282d4f-f5df-49f5-8ebc-477dfebab5dc">
<td data-local-id=3D"0b2a3b9b-b36c-400f-bae9-2fa748db3785" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"b03689c102f5">7</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"443f570f-d4c1-4da0-88bf-21986d85e3af" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"27244f983c3e">Add Note to Reservation</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"a667c8bb-b648-40c0-8c62-bd38b1872d50" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"f4fdc92b5697"><em>End of branch</em></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"643eb868-9276-41a2-a722-5a7cf863f820" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"7e6e011ab14b">Adds a note to all reservations where the upgr=
ade failed, so hotel staff can see which guests were not upgraded and why.<=
/p></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<hr local-id=3D"55633464-0572-4f79-b984-684375bd5ebe">
<h2 local-id=3D"49f8ca691630" id=3D"Upgraderoomforloyaltymembers(flow)-Comp=
onentDetails">Component Details</h2>
<p local-id=3D"591b064455f3">Below is a detailed breakdown of each componen=
t in the flow, including which fields are pre-configured and which can be c=
ustomized.</p>
<h3 local-id=3D"6f14de06335b" id=3D"Upgraderoomforloyaltymembers(flow)-1.Cr=
onScheduler">1. Cron Scheduler</h3>
<p local-id=3D"512d92d2fcee">The Cron Scheduler is a time-based trigger tha=
t starts the flow at regular intervals using standard cron syntax.</p>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-layout=3D"default" data-local-id=3D"4c16a26c-da6d-4722-a4cc-3cf=
2f1c5b51d" class=3D"confluenceTable">
<tbody>
<tr data-local-id=3D"8595a739-4990-4292-9c47-8e1ece26f442">
<th data-local-id=3D"a9de5156-4ec7-468a-a771-33088193bd7d" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"d57b1c3ac8ac">Field</p></th>
<th data-local-id=3D"8c6df0ea-a8f0-4b71-8f78-909d666db420" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"20cd61c39f78">Default Value</p></th>
<th data-local-id=3D"c50e41d6-0beb-4420-8b39-ba2511b03855" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"bdc705ef93df">Status</p></th>
<th data-local-id=3D"b54a85ec-9456-48e2-97d0-5f733bba347f" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"d25e0e7be48e">Description</p></th>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"70e50992-dc9d-4ad0-9167-296a72e708bc">
<td data-local-id=3D"03bb54e9-ef17-4df4-adac-aee4eaafaffb" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"d698a3749c86"><strong>Trigger immediately</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"ba0bc0c3-f5a2-4861-9346-ab0fd926555c" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"fb23ae35dd0a"><code>False</code></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"092ae22e-7b15-40bc-9f15-3d64fe5b3536" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"7b54d72e6fe9"><strong><span data-colorid=3D"hamctof2bn">Pre-=
filled</span></strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"eb15de49-ef2e-43f7-9f4d-879779ab297c" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"431e12cbe1aa">When set to true, the flow triggers once immed=
iately when started, in addition to the scheduled runs. Default is false =
=E2=80=94 the flow waits until the next scheduled time.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"b3a17667-7e1c-44a3-8f5e-668b5fa65eaa">
<td data-local-id=3D"245ea47d-9c5d-42ae-993d-9e3b1fe74d13" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"a74421541258"><strong>Minute</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"e0fbfe97-0be9-4f53-9968-a7b8b32c75f7" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"b5fdecd5bc56"><code>*</code></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"f121f840-f75c-4763-b63e-148d3bb68a33" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"b63b053d2e9e"><strong><span data-colorid=3D"hydnljan2l">Pre-=
filled</span></strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"a35c5c74-8f4a-4214-8f32-fda10df99eac" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"190ebcc35eb8">The minute of the hour to run. <code>*</code> =
means every minute (combined with the Hour setting, it runs at 12:00). Allo=
wed values: <code>*</code>, <code>-</code>, <code>/</code>, <code>0=E2=80=
=9359</code>.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"a0d63493-9ad7-4a83-9661-59478f2f0b9d">
<td data-local-id=3D"c3db6783-f313-4a27-abbc-aba07951a1ee" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"bfd878be8466"><strong>Hour</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"4a5e6ae4-1a6c-460a-9a06-3e3b0029c0b3" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"abb0e1a6c242"><code>12</code></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"f6f87909-2a34-4e13-b0cb-aeb53783c6c2" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"dbd06e86c41f"><strong><span data-colorid=3D"ky3w98l1kx">Pre-=
filled</span></strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"2684dc35-0564-47d2-9790-38d505e57f3f" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"4381bc5a08fc">The hour of the day to run. Set to <code>12</c=
ode> (noon). Allowed values: <code>*</code>, <code>-</code>, <code>/</code>=
, <code>0=E2=80=9323</code>.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"cf3e3fea-cb92-48c7-843b-ab8bf3950394">
<td data-local-id=3D"ddaa73cd-6234-4954-91eb-97843017ce50" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"5f55209a457c"><strong>Day of the Month</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"f749294f-e824-4dc4-90d3-5a3f07bcf25c" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"76f6254ebeb1"><code>*</code></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"3deb8c7b-99e3-4130-9ec8-d5cdac99f9a1" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"aa33abf5df6b"><strong><span data-colorid=3D"wel0ge6gt3">Pre-=
filled</span></strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"e268e7a6-bdb2-4632-a194-22625c35f9cf" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"637f53e95787">Which day(s) of the month to run. <code>*</cod=
e> means every day. Allowed values: <code>*</code>, <code>-</code>, <code>/=
</code>, <code>1=E2=80=9331</code>.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"dd9bd7b0-6b05-47c7-9eb0-9f6ceb5be807">
<td data-local-id=3D"26413a4e-fa94-411b-b816-895f5c2f24db" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"599128e46000"><strong>Day of the Week</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"9ac442e4-4373-45a6-80d9-fb4f1466a587" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"863760263e7b"><code>*</code></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"5ec511f0-e38b-479d-818d-3f9c3f282684" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"ceb236b24ee4"><strong><span data-colorid=3D"nqsd0ql3o5">Pre-=
filled</span></strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"35bd77d8-a11f-4ea7-903d-64bde56afa8c" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"1010b6b99852">Which day(s) of the week to run. <code>*</code=
> means every day. Allowed values: <code>*</code>, <code>-</code>, <code>/<=
/code>, <code>0=E2=80=936</code>, <code>SUN=E2=80=93SAT</code>.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"e2fc47c1-24ba-48a7-ba61-dfe5f4da420e">
<td data-local-id=3D"104b6920-d319-4fce-8d41-eff40f3f76c4" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"1f4014d65565"><strong>Timezone</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"ce781596-7d89-46c1-a658-481f0d583fa8" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"f13c1d628f47"><em>Empty</em></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"8740db6d-3741-485e-9f5b-36fcb37aeaba" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"18e86f7f8b01"><strong><span data-colorid=3D"qnwsk62aee">Pre-=
filled</span></strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"71622dcb-6141-40af-9a28-a6fef26c1106" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"d30132ccee53">The timezone for the schedule. When left empty=
, the schedule uses your local time. To use a specific timezone, enter a ti=
mezone identifier (e.g., <code>Europe/Prague</code>). By default it uses GM=
T.</p></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<p local-id=3D"13889deafe37"><strong>Default schedule:</strong> The flow is=
 pre-configured to run every day at 12:00 (noon). You can adjust the schedu=
le by changing the cron fields. For example, to run at 8:00 AM, change the =
Hour to <code>8</code>. To run only on weekdays, set Day of the Week to <co=
de>1-5</code> (Monday through Friday). If you want the schedule to run in y=
our local time, leave the Timezone field empty. To run in a specific timezo=
ne, enter the timezone identifier (e.g., <code>Europe/Prague</code>).</p>
<hr local-id=3D"537fabd1-cef1-4759-ba56-9dad76383798">
<h3 local-id=3D"9bd6da6d1ff4" id=3D"Upgraderoomforloyaltymembers(flow)-2.Ch=
eckOccupancy">2. Check Occupancy</h3>
<p local-id=3D"8586f0cacdb1">Calculates the current occupancy percentage fo=
r your property and determines whether there is enough capacity to proceed =
with upgrades. If occupancy is at or above the threshold, the flow stops an=
d no upgrades are attempted.</p>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-layout=3D"default" data-local-id=3D"14a367c5-6415-46e9-a551-3df=
99a6b6fac" class=3D"confluenceTable">
<tbody>
<tr data-local-id=3D"ab73bb2d-a010-413e-b471-dd000c50ad49">
<th data-local-id=3D"0f289392-ca61-4d03-937d-e561a32f9b43" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"268f83709015">Field</p></th>
<th data-local-id=3D"b27ac2ed-1ebb-4583-a722-cced9fba59c9" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"7c3e77f2863c">Default Value</p></th>
<th data-local-id=3D"44ef39dd-fcf5-4a08-afae-5ad870f67280" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"e4c2eceaefb8">Status</p></th>
<th data-local-id=3D"77ac7b9e-8f33-446b-84f8-0ea7950e1b0f" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"6f9e30bc5ac3">Description</p></th>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"c66741b7-2081-499e-880e-4d70dc25c6dc">
<td data-local-id=3D"7e3645dc-ad52-4a6b-ab6e-41acce3989bb" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"38699d003225"><strong>Date</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"41aec07f-7360-4a07-98ec-a6f03dad3b40" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"5d198ff4d1c7">Today's date</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"cd9b5c01-bc57-46be-b7db-c3101d3e0018" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"1ea7bebf64c2"><strong><span data-colorid=3D"enwah0dd2r">Pre-=
filled</span></strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"152d0b33-491d-4ba0-9177-ad7fa82344f6" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"111fb2ecbcda">The date to check occupancy for. Pre-filled to=
 use the current date.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"0c3b2701-eb6e-40b3-bb9e-10011d19198c">
<td data-local-id=3D"15de4bc2-b332-4fb3-a01b-bb9229b5ecb8" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"5df3afc8b728"><strong>Occupancy Percentage Threshold</strong=
></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"aedd4897-9ccd-48cf-9e67-81420d047ecf" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"a5c1435d0f9b"><code>100</code></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"c86b3ae6-0394-4538-943a-11b5e6cec818" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"7a30972ee337"><strong><span data-colorid=3D"r9by0fyhgp">Pre-=
filled</span></strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"ffebec7c-71ee-4d9d-988d-404edf6df541" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"953c468721b6">The occupancy percentage above which upgrades =
should not be attempted. Set to <code>100</code> by default, meaning upgrad=
es are only blocked when the property is completely full. You can lower thi=
s to be more conservative =E2=80=94 for example, setting it to <code>90</co=
de> would stop upgrades when 90% or more of rooms are occupied.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"e5924160-a17b-4275-b772-2f5471f13a4b">
<td data-local-id=3D"677cc1db-f897-47f1-a849-6f5a456530e6" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"da6c39cd3713"><strong>Bookable Services</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"a8232c13-d088-4e64-8623-abd5b1e0f7a2" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"7c594cb32e5a"><em>None selected</em></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"b40d9fd5-7c5a-4606-a0dd-264fe2fd2dd4" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"80168489a79a"><strong>Optional</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"a7a36c4e-2ef4-4f55-817e-fc497532b4f6" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"dc3cbeb413d8">Filter the occupancy calculation to specific b=
ookable services. If none are selected, all bookable services at the proper=
ty are included. Select specific services if you want the occupancy check t=
o consider only certain types of accommodations.</p></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<p local-id=3D"47ae93877875"><strong>How it connects:</strong> If occupancy=
 is <em>below</em> the threshold, the flow continues to <strong>Get Eligibl=
e Arrivals</strong>. If occupancy is <em>at or above</em> the threshold, th=
e flow stops =E2=80=94 no further components are executed.</p>
<hr local-id=3D"12dd077c-1715-4297-b890-260a2ff3edfc">
<h3 local-id=3D"dc989789b3f7" id=3D"Upgraderoomforloyaltymembers(flow)-3.Ge=
tEligibleArrivals">3. Get Eligible Arrivals</h3>
<p local-id=3D"370ad91a23d4">Retrieves confirmed reservations arriving on t=
he specified date. You can optionally filter guests by loyalty program memb=
ership, behavioral signals (stay frequency, revenue, recency), or rate code=
s to narrow down which reservations are eligible for an upgrade.</p>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-layout=3D"default" data-local-id=3D"c5e69e71-ef64-4665-bf4e-532=
4337d6655" class=3D"confluenceTable">
<tbody>
<tr data-local-id=3D"b5c97c59-f694-4fb5-8b71-a92b3f11cdec">
<th data-local-id=3D"e1fd0f7c-73f1-41a2-afb5-a94667f38ad9" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"4f3c4e7c27d5">Field</p></th>
<th data-local-id=3D"47227024-301e-4471-966d-4da1e7e15b5d" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"8bddf9b75c09">Default Value</p></th>
<th data-local-id=3D"3494f69d-9a7e-46ff-a072-59777191daec" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"b3e75ab07af2">Status</p></th>
<th data-local-id=3D"916a1efe-09db-4d20-891e-00368427a3d5" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"a5f194200b03">Description</p></th>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"06d9e2a6-4761-4d77-88ce-1bfe4e38842e">
<td data-local-id=3D"e69a4f2a-9921-4318-8c23-ea0dfa905f45" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"5d3593895bb2"><strong>Arrival Date</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"61cade28-4b86-4014-b0f7-5ac99315a1b2" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"07c5f7d5ec50">Today's date</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"ce752c29-e53b-4a36-883c-284b41f0a998" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"31715ea16f3f"><strong><span data-colorid=3D"o0n9uoiuxy">Pre-=
filled</span></strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"9ed99c88-b8af-4dce-8930-566bf5988218" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"f56b23523dc7">The date to search for arriving reservations. =
Pre-filled to use the current date so the flow always checks today's arriva=
ls. This can be adjusted if you need to look ahead to a future date.</p></t=
d>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"31378dbb-52cd-4c84-9124-52e175e85e71">
<td data-local-id=3D"cb4d095e-69dc-4720-ac18-752b1231e313" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"23fa24c1cc8b"><strong>Loyalty Programs</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"5365eee8-2709-40c8-9e4c-6c81f37a4e24" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"9f909bf8474b"><em>None selected</em></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"c4cfb71c-f727-4942-829f-1cfb7daf4c8f" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"d3c9770886e0"><strong>Optional</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"f3525653-678c-462c-a184-520e6f47e683" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"be6417e5c46c">Filter arrivals to guests enrolled in specific=
 loyalty programs. If no programs are selected, loyalty membership is not u=
sed as a filter criterion.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"b8961819-f16c-4875-9e3f-6b45cde0727a">
<td data-local-id=3D"fa1c6c27-5629-48ab-b758-dc98c17301aa" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"c547db18fd54"><strong>Loyalty Tiers</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"6d2d8478-c505-4ce3-9501-becd98af1dc8" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"1528ffa1a3f8"><em>None selected</em></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"3ae8c03b-e8f9-4299-901a-4f541fbfaeb7" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"7c9951e40adb"><strong>Optional</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"354c71a3-1f97-4a2b-89e4-96fc6c431f28" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"35f191c81c19">Further narrow the loyalty filter to specific =
tiers within the selected programs (e.g., Gold, Platinum). Only visible aft=
er a loyalty program is selected.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"aeaa7bef-d3ff-4eca-9088-f2126a322c83">
<td data-local-id=3D"49ae7d2e-2715-4423-ac73-1bb85a724c50" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"e64c83ab4643"><strong>Stay Count Threshold</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"d588e43c-5445-4382-aa9b-2bb37cea2315" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"271e06a5ae17"><em>Not set</em></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"7c0f0076-f68c-4d51-b87d-e33f46011afe" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"195443409922"><strong>Optional</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"65efc175-dcb9-4fcb-b597-004a7d98e7b4" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"1f911c532662">Minimum number of past stays a guest must have=
 to qualify. This is a behavioral signal =E2=80=94 guests who do not meet t=
he loyalty criteria can still qualify if they meet all configured behaviora=
l thresholds.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"d92bb459-8104-464d-92b2-386711b89df6">
<td data-local-id=3D"20b0d0f0-0ee7-427c-8d6c-fcd37a8c2dab" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"f87dd6e48bb9"><strong>Revenue Threshold</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"e9a844d0-bd6e-4ebc-9480-fb34eabf40e8" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"c6268c457437"><em>Not set</em></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"2412356b-2d86-4317-abac-7566c64c19fe" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"c5922282fe58"><strong>Optional</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"52719c69-1f0f-4eac-b9f4-58c8ffa3bbd4" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"7484c3f79e7c">Minimum total revenue (in the property's defau=
lt currency) a guest must have generated to qualify.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"d299d707-e12e-4a6f-b4c2-173ef030e3cf">
<td data-local-id=3D"0b525a90-e498-4a09-aee3-e001642d6127" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"bb6fce7f267c"><strong>Recency Threshold</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"4524ba9a-5791-4db4-bcc1-456c3a36ac57" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"02dee98b67f5"><em>Not set</em></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"9d06a4d7-a872-40ef-bdbe-47d31a084b2a" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"c86591116dab"><strong>Optional</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"18630c39-711e-4c9b-9b40-54c434958bf3" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"915531bd0289">Maximum number of days since the guest's most =
recent stay. Guests whose last stay was more recent than this threshold qua=
lify.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"a2a536d2-65c1-48e2-91f3-6788a719bc08">
<td data-local-id=3D"c3cd548d-e5b9-4913-a520-2459a7bdabf0" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"d4068ce9b9d5"><strong>Rates</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"b07a7de0-0bab-49bf-8154-71eee86ba0e8" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"f8a8237a17d9"><em>None selected</em></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"674d96bb-d5e5-48bd-bbcb-4a2315c780ef" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"6267af5266a4"><strong>Optional</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"6c5ce273-26d6-401e-9225-1e64725801c5" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"e5661ea4714a">Filter reservations by the rate they were book=
ed under. Only reservations matching the selected rates are included.</p></=
td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<p local-id=3D"cd08a033ff4a"><strong>Filtering logic:</strong> Guests are f=
irst evaluated against loyalty criteria (hard signals). If a guest is not p=
art of a selected loyalty program or tier, they are then evaluated against =
the behavioral thresholds (soft signals). A guest must meet <em>all</em> co=
nfigured behavioral thresholds to qualify. If no filters are configured, al=
l confirmed reservations with assigned rooms arriving on the specified date=
 are included.</p>
<hr local-id=3D"0543571b-b556-43ad-81b0-5bc1a4bc5bae">
<h3 local-id=3D"13d16b2fe2a7" id=3D"Upgraderoomforloyaltymembers(flow)-4.Up=
gradeAssignedRoomCategory">4. Upgrade Assigned Room Category</h3>
<p local-id=3D"e42e657bc0de">The core component of this flow. It takes the =
list of eligible reservation IDs and attempts to upgrade each guest's assig=
ned room category based on the upgrade paths you define. It checks real-tim=
e availability and respects buffer limits to ensure the property retains en=
ough rooms in each category.</p>
<p local-id=3D"d945d33bdb2f"><strong>Required configuration:</strong> You m=
ust configure the <strong>Upgrade Paths</strong> before the flow can run. T=
his is the only mandatory setup step for the entire flow.</p>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-layout=3D"default" data-local-id=3D"f8acdde1-978e-4f4c-9eb6-3ec=
6bbe54116" class=3D"confluenceTable">
<tbody>
<tr data-local-id=3D"4c640371-0c9d-4b00-a63d-7deefbad9227">
<th data-local-id=3D"1ee30c33-c87f-4631-8a73-416e5c5aab5c" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"c1f3e7dce47f">Field</p></th>
<th data-local-id=3D"27103aa1-1711-4797-892c-444b6db7615d" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"54a9d33e711a">Default Value</p></th>
<th data-local-id=3D"15b69836-c760-47b3-bfc6-134ac956aead" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"983afae06c0c">Status</p></th>
<th data-local-id=3D"b1406490-7721-4859-8837-1f49f4955ebb" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"3227e6b46fae">Description</p></th>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"2f8bf7b1-9cc8-4b60-b873-fbdbc2ae4cab">
<td data-local-id=3D"476fd8e3-cb08-40e4-be47-6c91f00d23a1" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"04e8c84f1636"><strong>Reservation IDs</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"c82269b0-a105-49a8-93b7-e457cfc6fc84" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"afc51fedf06b"><em>From previous step</em></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"11a517f6-390f-4251-85e9-b966aa301bd3" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"5882a6a3de11"><strong><span data-colorid=3D"q4zeo3kobi">Pre-=
filled</span></strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"af5f0146-953d-4964-bbdd-4401b937601d" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"e83a831ded0b">Automatically populated from the Get Eligible =
Arrivals output. Contains the list of reservation IDs to process for upgrad=
es.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"bdb6ad5d-4512-4d2b-985b-a6a6d54a731b">
<td data-local-id=3D"3258a682-3b65-4c28-a4fe-fade5956684f" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"4d477120ec39"><strong>Upgrade Paths</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"77114f21-1df8-459c-a203-3293be831b3c" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"2a5fc23940aa"><em>Not configured</em></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"62f6ceda-344e-41c2-980d-22cea448461c" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"6df7e386a40e"><strong>Required</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"b7aa540f-d8eb-4846-8cab-9dd4a15376fb" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"244a26fdb02b">Defines how room categories should be upgraded=
. Each row maps a source room category to a target room category (e.g., Sta=
ndard =E2=86=92 Deluxe). You can define multiple paths for cascading upgrad=
es (e.g., Standard =E2=86=92 Deluxe =E2=86=92 Suite). Each source category =
can only appear once. This must be configured before running the flow.</p><=
/td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"ac84c715-0fff-4e26-82db-d6d9b22edef5">
<td data-local-id=3D"667d141d-8b72-4f82-81c8-9500a361e01c" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"91d97104d652"><strong>Availability Buffer</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"c2b10160-54c5-4e62-adbe-6c4333fc59ad" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"2d499d7d8b04"><code>0</code></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"ab590ffa-04fd-4265-8b63-fdc1a0762516" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"cd75f21a3128"><strong><span data-colorid=3D"ld3eixs6u6">Pre-=
filled</span></strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"533f1bae-b4a9-480d-803b-f2e60e76cb16" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"aa58bc625375">The minimum number of rooms to keep available =
in the target category. Upgrades are only performed when enough rooms remai=
n above this buffer. Set to <code>0</code> by default, meaning all availabl=
e rooms can be used for upgrades. Increase this to reserve rooms for direct=
 bookings.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"5b1678d3-fe24-41a7-936c-ada84f70a2ae">
<td data-local-id=3D"01d12bf5-d71f-4ab5-975b-a0f5eb0d9718" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"8b07878910ad"><strong>Max Rooms to Upgrade</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"b106cb46-1205-4aab-aed7-9cefce717d23" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"5cce4dfe5657"><em>Not set</em></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"461dbbc4-9a9a-4fad-98ab-85d0ffa7a423" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"0b26ee0946c8"><strong>Optional</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"8ccadda4-d3fd-4f7f-9fad-70de96ae65eb" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"b379fedb246c">Maximum number of rooms to upgrade per run. On=
ce this limit is reached, remaining reservations are marked as failed with =
a <code>CAP_REACHED</code> reason. Leave empty for no limit.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"100340a0-6a9c-44db-9bf9-1b031db23251">
<td data-local-id=3D"e193449d-8389-416b-a871-ad4e7a187bee" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"590bbb24ea37"><strong>Per-Category Availability Overrides</s=
trong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"86d8b952-c278-4b78-a7bc-594dbd19b54f" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"43ebe53f39c8"><em>Not set</em></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"d616f3e9-dd30-4fb7-a001-e0da14d0e250" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"8d7fe03c46cd"><strong>Optional</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"888c4dd1-90ad-4fb2-828e-b000a5699b2c" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"d9056ad2ac5b">Found in the Advanced section. Override the gl=
obal availability buffer for specific room categories. Useful if some categ=
ories need a larger reserve than others.</p></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<p local-id=3D"6297f0ca9c81"><strong>Output ports:</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"e481744e-d363-43ba-92ef-f6a200cd3cb5">
<li local-id=3D"c628052a-166d-464e-80b7-19e499327c34">
<p local-id=3D"3bca70be7970"><strong>Upgraded:</strong> Fires when at least=
 one reservation was successfully upgraded. Passes the list of upgraded res=
ervation IDs to the <strong>Each</strong> iterator.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"44af644c-4484-43bd-899b-073b6c88be9d">
<p local-id=3D"ab78f065beae"><strong>Failed:</strong> Fires when at least o=
ne reservation could not be upgraded. Passes the list of failed reservation=
 IDs and failure reasons to <strong>Add Note to Reservation</strong>.</p></=
li>
<li local-id=3D"78b7f612-42dd-429b-bf8c-1c381ee6de0d">
<p local-id=3D"27814d6727e2"><strong>Cooldown:</strong> Fires when the comp=
onent's cooldown period is active, preventing duplicate upgrade attempts.</=
p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"e88c5d14-4afe-4d23-a8e0-416ebbfa097f">
<h3 local-id=3D"dcadff386db7" id=3D"Upgraderoomforloyaltymembers(flow)-5.Ea=
ch(Iterator)">5. Each (Iterator)</h3>
<p local-id=3D"94883b529c7c">The Each component receives the list of succes=
sfully upgraded reservation IDs and iterates over them one by one. For each=
 reservation, it triggers the <strong>Send SMS</strong> component so that e=
ach guest receives an individual notification.</p>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-layout=3D"default" data-local-id=3D"182e3db3-4551-42bd-8dae-722=
5e5648a16" class=3D"confluenceTable">
<tbody>
<tr data-local-id=3D"9cdad6b3-fba7-4e88-9fa0-549f2173fd6b">
<th data-local-id=3D"a74d9394-1c51-43ec-829f-17158807a0be" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"2292d0cf7894">Field</p></th>
<th data-local-id=3D"fc4382e9-983c-49a3-847c-940647b91edf" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"51b77c6a174f">Default Value</p></th>
<th data-local-id=3D"684e3e47-3850-4d59-86dd-c580471f5f37" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"cbc96f663ec3">Status</p></th>
<th data-local-id=3D"633d315b-23a1-469a-b1d3-67e74f9efb63" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"5f4f07e1ca01">Description</p></th>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"6594f847-daee-4b8c-9f87-e0aa98748a16">
<td data-local-id=3D"39309afb-e0f6-4919-a338-2cc29e3a944d" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"5622699f54ae"><strong>Field</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"7547fd8c-e21e-42ce-a6fb-399d6dcb3231" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"35ba3ff680fe">Upgraded Reservation IDs</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"e68a25bc-df64-4a11-87b8-7f515b82f23a" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"25f0246bc9cc"><strong><span data-colorid=3D"lzcnyzdb00">Pre-=
filled</span></strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"c214641f-054c-4c16-a285-191784de061d" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"752c123176cc">The list to iterate over. Pre-configured to us=
e the Upgraded Reservation IDs array from the Upgrade Assigned Room Categor=
y component.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"ae189b7e-b03e-43f7-8a16-1b427d17ad27">
<td data-local-id=3D"c6c7d4d2-9c53-41ff-8a2b-d2b1386f8c20" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"51f894c34d87"><strong>Delay</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"dfe4729c-bf44-4c09-8d8e-63c52893b496" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"f5c05979df60"><em>Not set</em></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"690ec3ee-efcc-4f41-9988-3572db696dd6" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"e8f3c1133f47"><strong>Optional</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"da7dadb6-6003-4443-b57f-bdb1db639ba8" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"4fa91097e113">Delay between processing each item, in millise=
conds. Can be used to add a pause between sending SMS messages if needed.</=
p></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<hr local-id=3D"1813e2ab-9d4e-407a-a4eb-bc964844f99b">
<h3 local-id=3D"0ede9c733cbc" id=3D"Upgraderoomforloyaltymembers(flow)-6.Se=
ndSMS">6. Send SMS</h3>
<p local-id=3D"059b3ee4e974">Sends an SMS message to the guest for each suc=
cessfully upgraded reservation. The guest is notified about their room upgr=
ade.</p>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-layout=3D"default" data-local-id=3D"6d74879d-b62f-4690-90ec-af9=
e548a0650" class=3D"confluenceTable">
<tbody>
<tr data-local-id=3D"36e543c1-be67-4781-a1ef-a66699d9af2a">
<th data-local-id=3D"0093abf1-de4f-42d6-acd6-4fc3633757c3" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"81ebe22705d4">Field</p></th>
<th data-local-id=3D"55d2a564-0d35-4b8b-8d11-60644b82f749" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"72d0c4976afb">Default Value</p></th>
<th data-local-id=3D"c54471a6-a87a-41f3-821a-819a7d03f11e" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"de6cc278c319">Status</p></th>
<th data-local-id=3D"e034d3a0-5deb-41ed-8a8f-02db69fd4fe3" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"255492386bce">Description</p></th>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"0c11e27c-41ed-45f8-a03c-de9fd0626d93">
<td data-local-id=3D"c1dc9c8a-f9e2-47ef-a2cc-0d76b98742fe" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"4abef6cf3b50"><strong>Guest ID</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"1df47d5a-adbf-4bfd-8e2e-4e998cee4dfc" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"54a136347950"><em>From previous step</em></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"dea90f2f-e470-4066-9ed5-80d0cb0aa207" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"02fe278b871d"><strong><span data-colorid=3D"fumasiiseq">Pre-=
filled</span></strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"c98f01f8-c12e-4335-bfa6-ac58cc0208cc" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"398e84540f66">Automatically populated from the upstream work=
flow data. Identifies which guest should receive the SMS.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"dbc8d613-54c0-4a64-839a-e9849e6dd445">
<td data-local-id=3D"547a3c3a-4298-45b3-95bc-f4fd19c19907" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"3fe5687cdb03"><strong>Reservation ID</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"e53bfa00-8720-4b12-8da4-4027decacdf8" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"bac39a4b924a"><em>From previous step</em></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"e7e07f0a-6354-4249-b2af-219df13b7f1d" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"53aa1589c350"><strong><span data-colorid=3D"iz0it71q6g">Pre-=
filled</span></strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"4a9242f4-812f-4237-ac6f-4ca0a7c33550" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"1690087fe63d">Automatically populated from the Each iterator=
. Links the SMS to the specific reservation.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"a912498d-b601-41a2-98bd-a0b9bfff7f6d">
<td data-local-id=3D"21decb74-5ce8-4e64-83ff-6c9f0362d4b8" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"cca9fe9aa3f3"><strong>Message body</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"56d370cc-f2e9-4800-969f-cf859d287bf0" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"c19a41f9692f"><em>Pre-filled template</em></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"2dd46ce5-8e11-4ff1-ac53-8ad26af550e7" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"56f5a62397cf"><strong><span data-colorid=3D"shp11a7k38">Pre-=
filled</span></strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"4c319b76-7ba6-4635-9aa2-fbdb785039f7" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"3041146cf856">The text content of the SMS. A default message=
 is included that informs the guest about their room upgrade. You can custo=
mize this message to match your property's tone and branding.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"22ddf3ab-6dfc-4be9-bf91-d855e047f39a">
<td data-local-id=3D"8eec770e-ad51-4ba4-94b7-00e99265b8ce" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"a448d9057d29"><strong>Sender</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"a073f5d2-a1ad-4597-86bc-3f0c932b2cdd" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"8fa8e33fddc7">Hotel</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"297cb1bf-eecc-497e-b88e-6a243abf273f" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"e8a3760c6890"><strong><span data-colorid=3D"lfb7b88grq">Pre-=
filled</span></strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"e1514953-59a0-4228-a99b-545e1012608f" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"ff0bdf6e39b0">Who the message is sent on behalf of. Set to <=
strong>Hotel</strong> by default. Can be changed to <strong>Guest</strong> =
if needed.</p></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<p local-id=3D"23da1315f580"><strong>Note:</strong> The SMS is sent to the =
phone number associated with the guest's profile. Ensure that guest profile=
s have valid phone numbers for SMS delivery to succeed.</p>
<hr local-id=3D"59c818c0-880a-4ffc-8dae-96b2ada0456b">
<h3 local-id=3D"182388c50158" id=3D"Upgraderoomforloyaltymembers(flow)-7.Ad=
dNotetoReservation">7. Add Note to Reservation</h3>
<p local-id=3D"432f1986a39e">For reservations where the upgrade failed, thi=
s component adds a note to each reservation. This ensures hotel staff can s=
ee which reservations were eligible for an upgrade but could not be process=
ed, along with the reason for the failure.</p>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-layout=3D"default" data-local-id=3D"98f57567-385a-499e-bc4f-a63=
12f912699" class=3D"confluenceTable">
<tbody>
<tr data-local-id=3D"18b6834e-5aa0-43a8-90a9-3431d8c0ed8b">
<th data-local-id=3D"077664a3-d23b-445b-9699-2b912c931a6f" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"a510cc4d4449">Field</p></th>
<th data-local-id=3D"fa546a5c-961b-4a1d-80d9-05b9551d2a1c" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"f52c0c5067ec">Default Value</p></th>
<th data-local-id=3D"19224510-8874-4370-8776-3b1b0f504403" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"9dc41a05be2f">Status</p></th>
<th data-local-id=3D"2e27fe4c-b9dc-4fce-b9e1-1e45deabdb82" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"ffa7694c954f">Description</p></th>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"1f0b44fe-4dd2-413e-879f-8e93995e5289">
<td data-local-id=3D"64399180-ca79-4eb3-81e8-30ef9e867976" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"d99d0d04986c"><strong>Reservation IDs</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"c2c11c48-8de1-4004-a346-3bfb7e77af5c" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"6318ae2d60fa"><em>From previous step</em></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"5c6984bc-3bcb-48c0-bb2a-133188fb5ce1" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"90974589a8bb"><strong><span data-colorid=3D"v5tgcdvlri">Pre-=
filled</span></strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"f1cb7a6a-11c5-4320-b188-3eddb9a5b328" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"9248d7cece92">Automatically populated with the list of reser=
vation IDs that failed to upgrade from the Upgrade Assigned Room Category c=
omponent.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"eee11382-fdb6-48ae-a910-d69d75a2c5b8">
<td data-local-id=3D"47d02542-8a2f-49f6-a2a3-eb1b4cf1cb03" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"b5aa08278768"><strong>Note Text</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"c47fe5ad-e846-4e44-a4e2-b3af63036dc0" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"d9c4227373ab"><em>Pre-filled template</em></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"456b92e0-9fd6-4836-b906-263a4c1c387f" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"764c2224e2e9"><strong><span data-colorid=3D"yx736bth0v">Pre-=
filled</span></strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"b6f73770-3a62-4ce1-86ec-a6153b023830" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"14af248428f8">The text of the note added to each reservation=
. A default message is included that describes the failed upgrade attempt. =
You can customize this to include additional instructions or context for yo=
ur team. Maximum 1,000 characters.</p></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<hr local-id=3D"e8988406-85b6-4786-8461-d15db8681583">
<h2 local-id=3D"fed102b13e78" id=3D"Upgraderoomforloyaltymembers(flow)-Setu=
pChecklist">Setup Checklist</h2>
<p local-id=3D"4ec2a2b22dcb">Use the following checklist to set up the flow=
 before running it for the first time:</p>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-layout=3D"default" data-local-id=3D"08457d04-d7f5-419a-ae3a-383=
d7c130c54" class=3D"confluenceTable">
<tbody>
<tr data-local-id=3D"0aed6dd6-0ab6-4a46-992c-28d01ca4aa9d">
<th data-local-id=3D"f0cd4f52-0393-44a0-8a11-132a2b09076e" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"d1280abbeb75">#</p></th>
<th data-local-id=3D"9588ec92-5da0-4db9-9a1e-91d417e01f0b" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"2a63e0997f29">Status</p></th>
<th data-local-id=3D"f51bac17-0955-415d-9263-c8fd65d60c99" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"971db10cfa16">Step</p></th>
<th data-local-id=3D"ec7109df-196d-4de7-ae60-e218cfad657a" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"d1ee9d7e526f">Details</p></th>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"b30ffad9-0e83-4817-a01f-4cc47c090e80">
<td data-local-id=3D"dd725e08-da1d-4d66-978a-d3c5ff0e26a3" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"8aa822d56761">1</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"2fa4c847-65a0-40de-bfbf-36fc5a17c715" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"51e6ad0b23a5"><strong>Required</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"faf5594d-75a1-4653-b84a-c0d0c736b59b" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"402325567738"><strong>Configure Upgrade Paths</strong></p></=
td>
<td data-local-id=3D"4b44feb9-3118-40a6-8d1a-e09d34ce7ac6" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"64e20b12fa2b">Open the <strong>Upgrade Assigned Room Categor=
y</strong> component and define your upgrade paths. Map each source room ca=
tegory to its target category (e.g., Standard =E2=86=92 Deluxe). You can ad=
d multiple rows for cascading upgrades.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"0f6563a3-ea9b-4159-a610-8e554acde1bc">
<td data-local-id=3D"19335ddf-f090-4331-825d-3d0cceee5ff0" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"d5d46b3f07ae">2</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"3ec1c566-4ce4-4bff-a887-320da303796a" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"bb8e94c8bc04"><strong>Optional</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"42543f09-e81b-467c-9599-0c54eddf94e7" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"3d1cc4648fbb">Adjust the schedule</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"6b40f5c5-834f-4bb8-b6a0-2c25aead228b" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"19c5e8ccd0b6">The flow runs daily at 12:00 (noon) by default=
. Modify the <strong>Cron Scheduler</strong> if you prefer a different time=
 or frequency.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"6ff6d445-2271-4785-9c35-9ee598b336b5">
<td data-local-id=3D"540fa6ac-8a3c-49b3-b032-f4b388bf0afa" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"62ce1cade00c">3</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"497964a1-bfad-4a7e-9a86-626e6165deb4" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"24ecbdb0db9e"><strong>Optional</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"751b9049-6f03-423f-86c7-bbc7e42476f3" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"4db6710b0a5a">Set occupancy threshold</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"1960f96b-8829-4409-9da9-ee889969f6f6" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"7162be023b52">The default is 100% (only stops when fully occ=
upied). Lower this in <strong>Check Occupancy</strong> if you want to be mo=
re conservative.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"9ae7192c-a6e7-497b-857c-1aa29b078337">
<td data-local-id=3D"9fb150af-dce8-444f-8d61-a18ccbcfa128" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"1be6b875be3a">4</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"05e42c46-c4e6-4f7e-b144-5e4efec07e12" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"70d5deaa475c"><strong>Optional</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"c620f1ef-c89a-4cd0-9a83-73483d583e2b" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"3dc01ebd32e9">Configure loyalty &amp; behavioral filters</p>=
</td>
<td data-local-id=3D"8c7243d2-1e42-4b39-a58e-2284eef05f53" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"e41e98fe2e2f">By default, all arriving guests are eligible. =
Add filters in <strong>Get Eligible Arrivals</strong> to target specific lo=
yalty programs, tiers, or behavioral segments.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"a9fae80e-b460-46f6-91fa-fe04ce1a386a">
<td data-local-id=3D"8ececb0b-050a-4f28-8224-02d701ff9e62" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"7bcfaedf595c">5</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"0e135688-dec8-45c5-bf6d-dc45c3ec2119" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"613c371bb340"><strong>Optional</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"34f735d4-09e1-4e2f-aa8d-53ae755d0596" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"2c48bebeb5fa">Set availability buffer</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"8f47e4bb-3a13-44f1-bac3-bb8a107caa8d" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"ae06455a19ed">The default buffer is <code>0</code> (no rooms=
 reserved). Increase this in <strong>Upgrade Assigned Room Category</strong=
> to retain rooms for direct bookings.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"66db8543-1a94-48f9-84c2-f9fa0d679a9e">
<td data-local-id=3D"c0005443-adf2-4bda-871e-001fb73daa23" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"e7cc9df2869d">6</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"e3575b1d-2a30-4ef9-97c6-c8ece72e1665" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"0475ad5ab5d9"><strong>Optional</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"72cc92b5-ebc7-454f-83fa-c6d2366bd818" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"c8d640283d2f">Customize SMS message</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"04d8e2e8-ab0e-48dd-b195-5952ce3cf771" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"44d42b870818">Edit the message body in <strong>Send SMS</str=
ong> to match your property's tone and branding.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"8b52d9a3-f736-472d-a269-2e6c23ac76f5">
<td data-local-id=3D"1927c9e8-452e-4622-afb2-3fc6b0833796" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"6dd296935004">7</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"573ac85b-5972-4ed2-9e15-8698c8b2be46" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"063581836920"><strong>Optional</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"c802e119-7cf8-4faa-b06b-a158a5e02de0" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"f4ecb3a8f32b">Customize reservation note</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"d9b1ee40-d39f-4622-a863-91eb0902997c" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"84aaa7e38589">Edit the note text in <strong>Add Note to Rese=
rvation</strong> to include additional context for your staff.</p></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<hr local-id=3D"f80617aa-e2ca-4794-ad3b-dedc0b418752">
<h2 local-id=3D"b942cda89a91" id=3D"Upgraderoomforloyaltymembers(flow)-Exam=
pleUseCases">Example Use Cases</h2>
<ul local-id=3D"c4a56799-0643-4360-bad8-7b272ecb3007">
<li local-id=3D"18b29f67-2509-4ccb-93da-f66f4cb4ef0e">
<p local-id=3D"4aa8ed9318b8"><strong>Loyalty-based upgrades:</strong> Confi=
gure the Get Eligible Arrivals component to filter by your loyalty program =
and Gold/Platinum tiers. Only your most loyal guests receive automatic upgr=
ades.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"d8d0be7e-35df-4334-880e-50c4858fb72f">
<p local-id=3D"125c1e40b626"><strong>High-value guest recognition:</strong>=
 Use the behavioral signal filters (revenue threshold, stay count) to autom=
atically upgrade frequent or high-spending guests, even if they are not enr=
olled in a loyalty program.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"5acf03cc-9f0c-4199-9ec9-3487c932e85c">
<p local-id=3D"ae23716d652e"><strong>Conservative upgrade policy:</strong> =
Set the occupancy threshold to 80% and the availability buffer to 2 to ensu=
re upgrades only happen when the property has plenty of capacity and at lea=
st 2 rooms remain available in each target category.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"2496b2b0-399b-414d-b118-c8a814e2606d">
<p local-id=3D"e5dd5c1cc0c2"><strong>Weekday-only upgrades:</strong> Modify=
 the Cron Scheduler to run only Monday through Friday by setting Day of the=
 Week to <code>1-5</code>, avoiding upgrades during peak weekend periods.</=
p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"a6e2a09a-d312-4329-bec8-b475b472908a">
<h2 local-id=3D"5738864d5bcc" id=3D"Upgraderoomforloyaltymembers(flow)-Trou=
bleshooting">Troubleshooting</h2>
<h4 local-id=3D"9a9b9d7912b8" id=3D"Upgraderoomforloyaltymembers(flow)-Thef=
lowrunsbutnoupgradeshappen">The flow runs but no upgrades happen</h4>
<ul local-id=3D"f94e23ba-e970-4f1f-ae86-b0cee3dc1145">
<li local-id=3D"a6837c99-6cdd-45e5-a022-14d5de1bf1af">
<p local-id=3D"ae13211954bf">Check that the <strong>Upgrade Paths</strong> =
are configured correctly and match existing room categories in your propert=
y.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"610a5d00-5849-42d3-9ccb-a77b3714f173">
<p local-id=3D"27072b3752de">Verify that there are arrivals for the current=
 date with assigned rooms in the source categories of your upgrade paths.</=
p></li>
<li local-id=3D"007cfca0-fe0f-428c-baaa-c58eb86b41ab">
<p local-id=3D"8de3b50c1aeb">Check the <strong>Check Occupancy</strong> com=
ponent =E2=80=94 if occupancy is above the threshold, the flow stops before=
 reaching the upgrade step.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"8b3afa17-33b5-4730-bfbb-eb3c08c9d7f4">
<p local-id=3D"47ac68cafbe0">If you configured loyalty or behavioral filter=
s, ensure that arriving guests meet the criteria.</p></li>
</ul>
<h4 local-id=3D"86078b3da21a" id=3D"Upgraderoomforloyaltymembers(flow)-Some=
reservationsfailtoupgrade">Some reservations fail to upgrade</h4>
<p local-id=3D"f1c715cf1895">Reservations may fail for the following reason=
s:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"d9eafe48-327c-47f7-94e0-a8af2a61795a">
<li local-id=3D"3bd27b6e-4bb1-4731-8540-2b4f27008495">
<p local-id=3D"ebb29614f1aa"><strong>NO_AVAILABILITY:</strong> There are no=
 available rooms in the target category (above the buffer threshold).</p></=
li>
<li local-id=3D"7eed792d-e493-462e-8cab-9799e072717a">
<p local-id=3D"f7cb652ccdfb"><strong>CAP_REACHED:</strong> The maximum numb=
er of upgrades per run has been reached.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"d79129e9-ab90-41d8-8af4-060def0fd559">
<p local-id=3D"727bb1819b89"><strong>NO_CATEGORY_FOUND:</strong> The reserv=
ation's current room category does not have a defined upgrade path.</p></li=
>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"c71a155d57ea">Failed reservations will have a note added aut=
omatically so your team can follow up manually if needed.</p>
<h4 local-id=3D"a100657189c5" id=3D"Upgraderoomforloyaltymembers(flow)-SMSm=
essagesarenotdelivered">SMS messages are not delivered</h4>
<ul local-id=3D"c19b10f7-232a-40e4-b622-ebad75861af4">
<li local-id=3D"6d2f595d-0f36-4268-b9a8-5854d55e43c5">
<p local-id=3D"6841b0cb4a94">Ensure that the guest profiles have valid phon=
e numbers configured.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"c26a6332-a8a0-41b2-9391-37ea2739e068">
<p local-id=3D"f8cd3c8366bc">Check that SMS messaging is enabled for your p=
roperty.</p></li>
</ul>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
